She's actually pretty
talented in a lot of ways.

60
00:05:07,416 --> 00:05:10,125
I mean, she can cook up
a mean rolled omelette

61
00:05:10,208 --> 00:05:11,458
and it looks
like she can cling

62
00:05:11,541 --> 00:05:13,500
to the window
without too much trouble.

63
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:25,541
Ayumu! We got a Megalo
sighting, so let's go!

64
00:05:25,625 --> 00:05:27,291
Okay! You don't have to yell!

65
00:05:28,541 --> 00:05:31,416
Whoops. Just got a
little too into it I guess.

66
00:05:33,833 --> 00:05:37,500
That's great so how am I
supposed to find this thing?

67
00:05:45,750 --> 00:05:47,166
I feel your pain.

68
00:05:50,250 --> 00:05:51,666
Yes, what is it?

69
00:05:51,750 --> 00:05:54,583
Sera? Are you able to
sense Megalos, like Haruna?

70
00:05:54,666 --> 00:05:57,958
I don't have that ability.
But hold on just a moment.

71
00:05:58,041 --> 00:06:00,500
Perhaps Lady Hellscythe
can help you.

72
00:06:00,583 --> 00:06:01,875
Cool, I'm sure she can.

73
00:06:01,958 --> 00:06:04,000
There's a block of
condos on 3rd street.

74
00:06:04,083 --> 00:06:06,375
Haruna and the megalo are
in the alley behind them.

75
00:06:06,458 --> 00:06:07,666
Great, thanks.

76
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:10,541
Wait. I have a message
from Lady Hellscythe.

77
00:06:10,625 --> 00:06:12,166
She says "hurry".

78
00:06:12,250 --> 00:06:13,500
Got it.

79
00:06:20,375 --> 00:06:22,166
Hey, this is Ayumu?

80
00:06:22,250 --> 00:06:24,625
I know, ma'am, you called me.

81
