That's right!
I'm calling because

82
00:06:27,333 --> 00:06:29,541
I need you to do
me a wittle bitty favor.

83
00:06:29,625 --> 00:06:32,041
Tell me what you
need and I am on it!

84
00:06:32,125 --> 00:06:33,708
Aw, you're just
like a little puppy,

85
00:06:33,791 --> 00:06:35,416
always just so eager to please.

86
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:37,958
Anyway I hate to bother you,
but there's something

87
00:06:38,041 --> 00:06:40,250
that I'd really love
for you to hold for me.

88
00:06:40,333 --> 00:06:41,791
It won't be long,
I just need for you

89
00:06:41,875 --> 00:06:44,583
to keep a finger on
it until I come, okay?

90
00:06:44,666 --> 00:06:47,125
What exactly are
we talking about here?

91
00:06:47,208 --> 00:06:49,250
I could try and explain it,
but I think that would be

92
00:06:49,333 --> 00:06:51,708
a waste of time.
It's very sensitive,

93
00:06:51,791 --> 00:06:55,125
so promise me you'll handle
it as delicately as possible.

94
00:06:55,208 --> 00:06:56,375
Oh-kay.

95
00:06:56,458 --> 00:06:58,125
Thank you so much!
It'll be coming

96
00:06:58,208 --> 00:07:00,375
in two shakes of a lamb's tail!

97
00:07:00,458 --> 00:07:04,375
And it's our little secret,
so don't tell Haruna! Bye bye!

98
00:07:08,958 --> 00:07:11,500
About one hundred
meters in direct sunlight.

99
00:07:11,583 --> 00:07:13,666
It's fly or fry time.

100
00:07:17,958 --> 00:07:20,375
Oh crap that's hot!
Hot hot hot!

101
00:07:20,458 --> 00:07:22,750
Come on, just a
little bit farther!

102
00:07:22,833 --> 00:07:25,041
Shade! Shade!

103
00:07:25,125 --> 00:07:26,083
I can't do it!

104
00:07:26,166 --> 00:07:30,750
It's killing me
for good! Bansai!

105
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:39,625
Man, that hurts!

106
00:07:39,708 --> 00:07:42,375
Aw, come on, don't be mad.

107
00:07:44,833 --> 00:07:47,291
Whoops! Nuh-uh! Missed me!

108
00:07:50,291 --> 00:07:51,125
Choke on it!

109
00:07:51,208 --> 00:07:53,250
So rank.

110
00:07:53,958 --> 00:07:56,333
I love it when they go down!

111
00:07:56,416 --> 00:08:00,083
Ohhhhh yeah! That's it!

112
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,041
There they are!

113
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,750
Ayumu!

114
00:08:09,833 --> 00:08:11,166
What the hell! Let go a me!

115
00:08:11,250 --> 00:08:13,291
What do you think you're
doing out here all by yourself?

116
00:08:13,375 --> 00:08:16,708
Well I was just... You
shoulda been here way sooner!

117
00:08:16,791 --> 00:08:19,625
It's okay, I got
here just in time!

118
00:08:20,833 --> 00:08:24,708
Take this, you
damn fly! Now buzz off!

119
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,333
That did the trick!

120
00:08:43,750 --> 00:08:46,166
Hurry up and transform
for cryin' out loud!

121
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:48,875
That thing is a
class double-A megalo!

122
00:08:48,958 --> 00:08:52,166
He's the super scary
horse beast, Wanderlei Siuma!

123
00:08:52,250 --> 00:08:53,791
No more horsin' around!

124
00:08:53,875 --> 00:08:56,708
So, I guess I gotta do this.

125
00:08:57,125 --> 00:09:00,958
Nomobuyo. Oshi. Hashitawa.

126
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:06,791
Dokeda. Gunmiicha. Deh Ribura.

127
00:09:06,875 --> 00:09:12,458
Oh yeah. That's it! Oh my God!

128
00:09:13,333 --> 00:09:16,291
Alright! Now I feel
like a man again!

129
00:09:16,375 --> 00:09:17,333
You want some?

130
00:09:17,416 --> 00:09:18,833
Yes! Yes! I'm gonna
make you squeal!

131
00:09:18,916 --> 00:09:20,458
Look out! Behind you!

132
00:09:23,666 --> 00:09:25,750
Yeah! More, baby! More!

133
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:30,125
Hey listen! I'm really not
kidding here! Look out!

134
00:09:33,125 --> 00:09:34,125
I told you!

135
00:09:34,208 --> 00:09:36,500
I like to call
this move "the shocker".

136
00:09:39,875 --> 00:09:43,750
Calm down.
Let me see. Where is it?

137
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:45,250
Ooh, just a little tickle.

138
00:09:48,458 --> 00:09:50,583
Oohh yuck yuck!
Not what I wanted.

139
00:09:50,666 --> 00:09:52,125
Bad touch! Bad touch!

140
00:09:54,708 --> 00:09:57,458
Now that's more like it!
Give me some sugar!

141
00:09:57,541 --> 00:10:00,375
Hey! Get your
slimy paws offa me!

142
00:10:00,458 --> 00:10:02,333
Let go of her!

143
00:10:02,416 --> 00:10:04,958
Yeah. That's it.
Don't be stingy!

144
00:10:06,458 --> 00:10:07,833
Please! Somebody!

145
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:10,250
I don't care who! Help!

146
00:10:12,208 --> 00:10:13,500
Sorry to keep you waiting.

147
00:10:13,583 --> 00:10:15,500
What the? Who are you?

148
00:10:15,583 --> 00:10:16,791
Here ya go.

149
00:10:27,375 --> 00:10:29,583
Did that? No way?

150
00:10:29,666 --> 00:10:31,083
OWEE! Noooo!

151
00:10:31,166 --> 00:10:34,791
I don't believe it.
He's killing those megalos.

152
00:10:34,875 --> 00:10:37,000
With bowls of ramen?!

153
00:10:38,208 --> 00:10:39,833
Oh! What a world!
What a world!

154
00:10:40,833 --> 00:10:43,375
No! Please don't!

155
00:10:43,958 --> 00:10:46,875
Holy crap, that must
be some really bad ramen.

156
00:10:46,958 --> 00:10:48,916
They can't take it at all.

157
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,541
You forgot about me!

158
00:10:54,875 --> 00:10:58,458
Seraphim! It's great
to see you again!

159
00:10:58,541 --> 00:10:59,583
It's been so lo--

160
00:11:01,458 --> 00:11:03,583
Do not approach me
as if we are friends.

161
00:11:03,666 --> 00:11:06,958
Ow. Seraphim,
that hurts! Let go!

162
00:11:07,041 --> 00:11:09,125
Please! You're gonna
break my arm!

163
00:11:09,208 --> 00:11:10,833
Sera. You know this dude?

164
00:11:10,916 --> 00:11:12,916
This is an
acquaintance of mine, yes.

165
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:14,041
Well, he saved our asses,

166
00:11:14,125 --> 00:11:16,500
so the least you
could do is let him go.

167
00:11:16,583 --> 00:11:17,750
Who is it, by the way?

168
00:11:17,833 --> 00:11:19,625
They go by the name, Mael Strom.

169
00:11:19,708 --> 00:11:22,125
A Vampire Ninja,
aligned with a reformist faction

170
00:11:22,208 --> 00:11:24,541
I do not care for one iota.

171
00:11:24,875 --> 00:11:27,250
Geez, Seraphim.
What in the hell?

172
00:11:27,333 --> 00:11:29,791
Were you tryin' ta
break my arm for real?

173
00:11:29,875 --> 00:11:32,166
He's right. You went kinda nuts.

174
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:33,208
Hey, are you alright?

175
00:11:33,291 --> 00:11:34,041
Don't touch me!

176
00:11:34,125 --> 00:11:35,458
Leave 'em alone.

177
00:11:35,541 --> 00:11:37,041
The megalos are gone,
so we should just go back home.

178
