ya little brat!

184
00:11:46,541 --> 00:11:48,083
No way! I'm a high schooler!

185
00:11:48,166 --> 00:11:49,666
You're way too
little to be in my class!

186
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:51,958
Hey! Listen to me!

187
00:11:52,041 --> 00:11:54,750
I'm talkin'
over here, you dumbass!

188
00:12:08,041 --> 00:12:10,500
