189
00:12:12,583 --> 00:12:15,458
Oh baby,
I think I'm coming, too!

190
00:12:21,666 --> 00:12:25,250
My first kiss,
and it's a dude? Uhh.

191
00:12:38,958 --> 00:12:42,291
