witness something so foul!

194
00:12:46,125 --> 00:12:47,750
If you're gonna go
around tongue-raping people

195
00:12:47,833 --> 00:12:48,958
out of the blue like that,

196
00:12:49,041 --> 00:12:51,125
have the decency to
brush your teeth first!

197
00:12:51,208 --> 00:12:53,958
Right. Please
forgive me, ma'am.

198
00:13:03,375 --> 00:13:06,041
Our secret base
is behind these doors.

199
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:08,666
Inside this factory?

200
00:13:09,083 --> 00:13:11,250
Well, yeah.
You said you wanted to see

201
00:13:11,333 --> 00:13:13,375
